data.description:
This home has it all, brand new hot water heater, brand new HVAC, 1 year old roof, 2-3 year old appliances, a pool, and it's all sitting on .6 acres!!
Step into a welcoming living room that seamlessly connects to a cozy den with a wood burning fireplace. The Kitchen provides ample cabinet space with 2-3 year old stainless steel appliances. 
Enjoy the best of indoor-outdoor living with a large screened-in porch. Outside, a refreshing above-ground pool with ample space for entertaining. A little TLC will transform this home into your personal haven.
